msgid "micchāsatiyā paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from wrong mindfulness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc13
msgctxt "an10.119:13.1"
msgid "… ‘Micchāsamādhissa kho pāpako vipāko—"
msgstr "‘Wrong immersion has a bad result "

