msgstr "Reflecting like this, they give up wrong freedom, "

msgctxt "an10.119:15.4"
msgid "micchāvimuttiyā paccorohati. "
msgstr "they descend from wrong freedom. "

msgctxt "an10.119:15.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇī hotī”ti. "
msgstr "This is the ceremony of descent in the training of the noble one.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.236, sc16
msgctxt "an10.119:16.1"
msgid "“Aññathā, bho gotama, brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī, aññathā ca pana ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇī hoti. "
msgstr "“The ceremony of descent observed by the brahmins is quite different from that observed in the training of the noble one. "

msgctxt "an10.119:16.2"
msgid "Imissā ca, bho gotama, ariyassa vinaye paccorohaṇiyā brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī kalaṃ nāgghati soḷasiṃ. "
msgstr "And, Master Gotama, the ceremony of descent observed by the brahmins is not worth a sixteenth part of a master of the ceremony of descent observed in the training of the noble one. "

msgctxt "an10.119:16.3"
msgid "Abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "Excellent, Master Gotama! … "

msgctxt "an10.119:16.4"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.119:16.5"
msgid "Sattamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

